{"tid":1628144,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(文宣) 大家破壞左黨鐵，另一邊可以教人搭其他交通工具","createTime":"2019-10-06T00:51:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T00:59:09.000Z","uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"12f2c276b597bdcebcaeed3dc559dbce363a36f3","tid":1628144,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:51:01.000Z","msg":"依家881 May姐話基層唔識搭巴士， 星期日返唔到工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然呢個年代人人有部iphone的確係冇咩可能既事，但如果我地做多一步， 出文宣教大眾罷搭黨鐵同時， 有咩巴士去到想去既地方， 係咪好好呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2個app一定要裝：<br />\n九巴app (唔洗講啦基本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n中原地圖app<br />\n呢個好重要， 佢可以顯示附近地區有咩巴士站，巴士路線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n圖片舉例：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pe9JKjG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPe9JKjG.png&h=2ddc6f71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n解散警隊<br />\n拯救香港"},{"pid":"317be8cca50991bf2de0ddd951c028e744c99878","tid":1628144,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"推阿， 爭取民意好重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba7c3f927c0559cf76c5a869924282966692c902","tid":1628144,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:53:30.000Z","msg":"再推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4427c4991ebc1ab2bd426d9fce326b2847a806d","tid":1628144,"uid":159246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T00:59:09.000Z","msg":"十連<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}